支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4XXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=7d12dc37\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4XXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=e9fa204f\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4XXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=7653b454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>區議會選舉經費大籌集</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678412/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678412/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a8a61d63b6f2bc1c217463e1ca556c5212eeb048","tid":1678430,"uid":322922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"唔係想指揮前線，但唔該要睇時間快閃，少你地任何一個都唔想呀，快閃爆破完就要閃，街坊就盡留撚狗，一來幫前線爭取時間，二來擋到幾多就幾多，街坊唔怕俾人拉下話"},{"pid":"8f999ec745552661c7d16f04fc2cd9e0134361cd","tid":1678430,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"有「速龍」由私家車下車，車牌號碼為UY2745、UN7295、VX2547、UZ6714及AM7093。"},{"pid":"f1f4c6b8304d317dc7eaefc9f086f4edfd4c7c17","tid":1678430,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:17:56.000Z","msg":"有人暈左 比人搬左上去私家車"},{"pid":"4fb8ff30f3eafaa6e38fdaa218c2f082807b900f","tid":1678430,"uid":138609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1f4c6b8304d317dc7eaefc9f086f4edfd4c7c17","tid":1678430,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:17:56.000Z","msg":"有人暈左 比人搬左上去私家車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:18:45.000Z","msg":"上左AM7093<br />\n記者朋友要跟住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060388e972434db19f86bcf83bc2394bafe8e081","tid":1678430,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:20:50.000Z","msg":"又有卧底狗<br />\n好彩影到少少樣"},{"pid":"a4f4c8ce9082ce3f30638653cf8f6087c12758b0","tid":1678430,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:27:00.000Z","msg":"唔係次次一定要留到咁夜。"},{"pid":"db7e9ebb01ce00b800460c49ea6b7eb242a5a95a","tid":1678430,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:30:02.000Z","msg":"唔好陪臥底 留咁夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.